data.title: HUGE MEDIEVAL NIGHT SIEGE - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay
data.description:
Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay - It's the Hundred years war.  And the French begin their counter attack to take back their lands that were conquered by the English! The French first objective is to take an English Stronghold, they have been sieging it for 6 months, but plan for a full on assault at night!  Enjoy the battle :D

Jackie's POV: http://youtu.be/dvlNxhTw1jQ

This is Goodrich Castle
Download the Map:
